    "en": {
      "title": "Change in fuel delivery days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power and Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekara has said that the fuel distribution days have been changed based on the last digit of the vehicle number plate.",
        "According to the minister, the fuel supply will be implemented on the final digits 0,1,2 - Tuesday and Saturday, 3,4,5 - Thursday and Sunday, 6,7,8,9 - Monday, Wednesday and Friday.",
        "The minister also said that the QR code issued under the National Fuel Permit will be tested from July 21 to July 24 at some locations in Colombo.",
        "He informed that nearly 2 million people have registered for the National Fuel Permit at 4.00 pm today and the QR system will be implemented across the country from July 25."
      ],
